useradd <user>
usermod -a -G <sudogroup>


wget https://github.com/<user>/<repo>/archive/<branch>.tar.gz

using .tgz 

wget https://github.com/<user>/<repo>/archive/<branch>.tar.gz


Using cURL
curl -L https://github.com/<user>/<repo>/archive/<branch>.zip

For even more control, go to github webpage and just the download address for any download link and use that address.
